<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Episode 24)</i></font>

5
00:00:18,999 --> 00:00:21,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa wali pasien dekat ruang operasi?</font>

6
00:00:23,139 --> 00:00:24,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Song Eun Jae...,</font>

7
00:00:24,609 --> 00:00:25,970
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau tidak dengar aku menyuruhmu keluar?</font>

8
00:00:28,979 --> 00:00:30,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya dokter bodoh ini...</font>

9
00:00:30,780 --> 00:00:33,149
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak tahu letak ruang tunggu.</font>

10
00:00:33,410 --> 00:00:36,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Direktur, maukah kau
menunjukkan jalan padanya?</font>

11
00:00:36,550 --> 00:00:37,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

12
00:00:37,889 --> 00:00:39,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu saja.</font>

13
00:00:42,319 --> 00:00:44,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Song, ikut aku ke luar.</font>

14
00:00:50,160 --> 00:00:51,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih...,</font>

15
00:00:52,770 --> 00:00:53,869
<font color=#FFFF00>...Profesor.</font>

16
00:00:56,369 --> 00:00:57,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong rawat...</font>

17
00:01:00,579 --> 00:01:01,939
<font color=#FFFF00>...ayahku dengan baik.</font>

18
00:01:09,949 --> 00:01:11,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Song, mari kita ke luar.</font>

19
00:01:37,009 --> 00:01:39,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita akan memulai bedah <i>reseksi</i>...</font>

20
00:01:39,009 --> 00:01:41,619
<font color=#FFFF00><i>duodenum hepaticopancreatic</i>
pasien Song Jae Joon.</font>

21
00:01:42,750 --> 00:01:45,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Lemaskan otot bahu dan leher kalian.</font>

22
00:01:46,490 --> 00:01:47,819
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini operasi yang kita lakukan setiap hari.</font>

23
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:50,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian tidak boleh gugup
karena ayah dokter Song.</font>

24
00:01:51,929 --> 00:01:52,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengerti.</font>

25
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:56,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Kim Jae Hwan, kau mengerti?</font>

26
00:01:57,929 --> 00:02:00,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu saja.</font>

27
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,699
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita mulai.</font>

28
00:02:05,569 --> 00:02:06,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Pisau bedah.</font>

29
00:02:10,909 --> 00:02:13,179
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Ruang operasi)</i></font>

30
00:02:16,349 --> 00:02:17,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa? Kenapa kau sudah kembali?</font>

31
00:02:18,890 --> 00:02:21,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada masalah pada ayah?
/ Tidak.</font>

32
00:02:22,290 --> 00:02:24,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka melanjutkan operasi
seperti yang direncanakan.</font>

33
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:26,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi... tapi kenapa kau di sini?</font>

34
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Ceritnya panjang.</font>

35
00:02:50,890 --> 00:02:52,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini. Makan itu nanti.</font>

36
00:02:53,290 --> 00:02:55,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus melakukan upacara peringatan
untuk kakek-nenek kita dulu.</font>

37
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi aku lapar.</font>

38
00:02:59,330 --> 00:03:00,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada yang memberiku makanan.</font>

39
00:03:17,409 --> 00:03:19,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah dokter Song...</font>

40
00:03:20,379 --> 00:03:21,379
<font color=#FFFF00>...sedang dioperasi.</font>

41
00:03:25,820 --> 00:03:28,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika Ayah tidak sakit, Ayah pasti...</font>

42
00:03:30,189 --> 00:03:32,290
<font color=#FFFF00>...langsung menyetujui operasinya.</font>

43
00:03:35,129 --> 00:03:36,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Maka...,</font>

44
00:03:39,869 --> 00:03:42,270
<font color=#FFFF00>...dokter Song tidak akan sangat khawatir.</font>

45
00:03:45,570 --> 00:03:46,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar?</font>

46
00:04:21,409 --> 00:04:23,440
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Kim Jae Min, "Aku selalu mencintaimu, Nak.")</i></font>

47
00:04:41,229 --> 00:04:42,299
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemari.</font>

48
00:04:43,729 --> 00:04:45,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemari dan...</font>

49
00:04:46,500 --> 00:04:48,140
<font color=#FFFF00>...berikan pada kakakmu.</font>

50
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:50,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Berikan padanya...</font>

51
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:54,279
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan beri salam.</font>

52
00:05:00,450 --> 00:05:03,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergilah. Jangan buat Ibumu menunggu.</font>

53
00:05:05,219 --> 00:05:06,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergi dan beri salam.</font>

54
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:11,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau belum pernah ke sini
sejak kakakmu meninggal.</font>

55
00:05:12,930 --> 00:05:16,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pasti sangat merindukanmu.</font>

56
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:35,380
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Kim Jae Min. Kami mencintaimu, Nak.)</i></font>

57
00:05:51,270 --> 00:05:52,669
<font color=#FFFF00>Sayang.
/ Jae Geol.</font>

58
00:05:58,409 --> 00:05:59,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Tetap disini.</font>

59
00:06:17,359 --> 00:06:19,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sedang apa di sini?</font>

60
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:22,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah benar.</font>

61
00:06:25,229 --> 00:06:26,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah membunuh Jae Min.</font>

62
00:06:28,599 --> 00:06:31,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah membunuhnya.
/ Kau tidak membunuhnya.</font>

63
00:06:37,849 --> 00:06:40,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau saja aku tidak meneleponnya.</font>

64
00:06:41,919 --> 00:06:43,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika aku tidak memintanya untuk...</font>

65
00:06:45,149 --> 00:06:47,289
<font color=#FFFF00>...menjemputku di bandara saat hujan.</font>

66
00:06:49,989 --> 00:06:53,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika saja aku tidak bepergian
ke tempat seperti India agar...</font>

67
00:06:54,899 --> 00:06:56,859
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku bisa menyombongkan diri.</font>

68
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:02,039
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang membuatmu
ingin meninggalkan rumah dan Korea?</font>

69
00:07:03,909 --> 00:07:05,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang membandingkanmu
dengan Jae Min...</font>

70
00:07:06,210 --> 00:07:09,010
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan membuatmu merasa rendah diri?</font>

71
00:07:11,149 --> 00:07:12,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu...,</font>

72
00:07:12,649 --> 00:07:16,250
<font color=#FFFF00>...Aku salah karena sudah memarahimu.</font>

73
00:07:16,250 --> 00:07:17,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

74
00:07:21,159 --> 00:07:22,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku marah.</font>

75
00:07:24,789 --> 00:07:27,799
<font color=#FFFF00>Kehilangan kakakmu
secara mendadak seperti itu...</font>

76
00:07:27,799 --> 00:07:29,399
<font color=#FFFF00>...membuatku sangat marah.</font>

77
00:07:31,529 --> 00:07:33,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak tahan.</font>

78
00:07:35,770 --> 00:07:37,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus melampiaskan
kemarahanku pada seseorang...</font>

79
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:41,479
<font color=#FFFF00>...supaya aku bisa bertahan hidup.</font>

80
00:07:48,279 --> 00:07:51,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku seharusnya tidak
memperlakukanmu seperti itu.</font>

81
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:54,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Salahku...</font>

82
00:07:55,219 --> 00:07:57,359
<font color=#FFFF00>...melakukan itu pada anakku sendiri.</font>

83
00:07:57,659 --> 00:07:58,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

84
00:08:00,659 --> 00:08:02,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu keadilan.</font>

85
00:08:04,229 --> 00:08:06,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Jae Min meninggal karena diriku.</font>

86
00:08:07,669 --> 00:08:09,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi Ayah...
/ Hentikan.</font>

87
00:08:16,539 --> 00:08:17,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Kim.</font>

88
00:08:17,979 --> 00:08:20,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Berikan pendapatmu sebagai dokter.</font>

89
00:08:22,580 --> 00:08:24,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa penyebab kematian Kim Jae Min?</font>

90
00:08:25,149 --> 00:08:26,649
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.
/ Kakakmu.</font>

91
00:08:27,489 --> 00:08:29,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan bicara padaku sebagai adiknya.</font>

92
00:08:29,690 --> 00:08:32,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebagai dokter yang terakhir
mendiagnosa pasien sekarat...,</font>

93
00:08:33,900 --> 00:08:35,200
<font color=#FFFF00>...berikan pendapatmu.</font>

94
00:08:36,629 --> 00:08:38,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa penyebab kematian?</font>

95
00:08:48,379 --> 00:08:49,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena kecelakaan lalu lintas...,</font>

96
00:08:52,180 --> 00:08:54,080
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia menderita patah tulang...</font>

97
00:08:56,619 --> 00:08:57,790
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan pendarahan otak...</font>

98
00:08:59,290 --> 00:09:00,790
<font color=#FFFF00>...disebabkan oleh trauma eksternal.</font>

99
00:09:04,489 --> 00:09:07,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar. Aku setuju dengan hasil itu.</font>

100
00:09:08,460 --> 00:09:11,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi mulai sekarang, jangan lupa.</font>

101
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakakmu...</font>

102
00:09:14,139 --> 00:09:15,670
<font color=#FFFF00>...bukan mati karena dirimu.</font>

103
00:10:18,570 --> 00:10:21,670
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Rumah Sakit Jeil Geoje)</i></font>

104
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:24,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei.
/ Pak Chu.</font>

105
00:10:24,170 --> 00:10:26,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa?</font>

106
00:10:26,170 --> 00:10:27,509
<font color=#FFFF00>Baru saja dimulai.</font>

107
00:10:27,509 --> 00:10:29,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Kesulitannya, 12-jam.</font>

108
00:10:30,580 --> 00:10:32,150
<font color=#FFFF00>12 jam?</font>

109
00:10:32,150 --> 00:10:34,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu tergantung pada kondisi pasien.</font>

110
00:10:39,050 --> 00:10:41,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sedang apa di sini?</font>

111
00:10:41,389 --> 00:10:43,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah kau bilang
akan menemui anak-anak?</font>

112
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:45,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Emm...</font>

113
00:11:16,460 --> 00:11:17,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa?</font>

114
00:11:18,859 --> 00:11:21,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini aku.
/ Apa maumu?</font>

115
00:11:23,330 --> 00:11:25,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini Chuseok. Aku ingin bertemu anak-anak.</font>

116
00:11:28,700 --> 00:11:30,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka tidak ada.</font>

117
00:11:30,369 --> 00:11:32,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka sedang di perpustakaan,
belajar untuk ujian tengah semester.</font>

118
00:11:32,239 --> 00:11:34,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisakah kau memberi mereka
istirahat di hari libur?</font>

119
00:11:34,979 --> 00:11:37,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Siswa perlu mengambil istirahat untuk...</font>

120
00:11:37,180 --> 00:11:38,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana jika mereka melakukannya?</font>

121
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:41,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita berpisah dan tidak mampu
untuk memberi mereka...</font>

122
00:11:41,979 --> 00:11:43,619
<font color=#FFFF00>...guru privat atau kelas.</font>

123
00:11:44,190 --> 00:11:46,519
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka akan jadi apa jika tidak belajar?</font>

124
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:48,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Sayang.
/ Jangan panggil aku itu.</font>

125
00:11:49,859 --> 00:11:52,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita sudah menandatangani
surat cerai tujuh tahun yang lalu.</font>

126
00:11:52,930 --> 00:11:56,599
<font color=#FFFF00>Tintanya tidak hanya kering. Sudah memudar.</font>

127
00:11:56,599 --> 00:11:59,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau ingin datang setiap saat...</font>

128
00:11:59,670 --> 00:12:02,700
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan berpura-pura jadi ayah yang peduli
saat kau tidak bisa menawarkan apa-apa lagi...,</font>

129
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:03,910
<font color=#FFFF00>...jangan pernah datang lagi.</font>

130
00:12:04,139 --> 00:12:06,469
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya...
/ Saat mereka tumbuh...,</font>

131
00:12:07,580 --> 00:12:10,180
<font color=#FFFF00>...anak-anak akan mencarimu
meskipun aku melarang mereka.</font>

132
00:12:10,180 --> 00:12:12,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi jangan membuat mereka bingung
dengan berkunjung.</font>

133
00:12:19,950 --> 00:12:20,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini?</font>

134
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:23,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Bonus Chuseok-ku dan uang saku...</font>

135
00:12:23,460 --> 00:12:25,330
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk anak-anak.</font>

136
00:12:42,910 --> 00:12:45,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau seharusnya tidak bekerja sangat keras.</font>

137
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:48,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau seharusnya meninggalkan
kapal rumah sakit setelah 10 tahun.</font>

138
00:12:50,389 --> 00:12:52,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah memikirkannya...,</font>

139
00:12:52,950 --> 00:12:55,859
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi saat waktunya tiba,
Aku tidak mau pergi.</font>

140
00:12:56,219 --> 00:12:57,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu bukan berarti kalau kau tidak mau.</font>

141
00:12:58,430 --> 00:13:00,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak bisa.</font>

142
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasien untuk diperhatikan...</font>

143
00:13:02,830 --> 00:13:05,469
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan dokter muda
untuk dibina pemikirannya.</font>

144
00:13:06,269 --> 00:13:09,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak punya waktu untuk pergi.</font>

145
00:13:09,940 --> 00:13:13,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan sekarang,
kau membawakan kami ahli bedah.</font>

146
00:13:15,780 --> 00:13:18,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Terlepas dari perkataan orang...,</font>

147
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:20,680
<font color=#FFFF00>...kapal kita bisa sejauh ini berkat dirimu.</font>

148
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:23,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Dulu, bisa saja kita terdampar.</font>

149
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:26,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu murni omong kosong.</font>

150
00:13:27,460 --> 00:13:30,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Periksa ponselmu.
Sudah berdering dari tadi.</font>

151
00:13:30,359 --> 00:13:32,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, benar.
/ Ini.</font>

152
00:13:34,930 --> 00:13:37,369
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Hiburlah dia.
/ Anda sedang bersama dia?</i></font>

153
00:13:37,369 --> 00:13:38,670
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku akan ke sana jika bukan hari Chuseok.</i></font>

154
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:41,969
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bagaimana dengan ayah Dokter Song?</i></font>

155
00:13:42,170 --> 00:13:43,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu?</font>

156
00:13:44,170 --> 00:13:47,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Para dokter dan staf kapal.</font>

157
00:13:47,509 --> 00:13:49,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka menanyakan kabar ayah Dokter Song.</font>

158
00:13:49,940 --> 00:13:52,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Lihat? Seperti itulah mereka.</font>

159
00:13:52,009 --> 00:13:54,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka semua pergi berlibur...,</font>

160
00:13:54,119 --> 00:13:57,190
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan mereka menganggapmu
berada di rumah sakit.</font>

161
00:14:01,989 --> 00:14:03,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau marah...,</font>

162
00:14:03,489 --> 00:14:07,060
<font color=#FFFF00>...cobalah untuk berhenti, dan bergembira.</font>

163
00:14:07,830 --> 00:14:11,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau punya sangat banyak pengikut.</font>

164
00:14:19,509 --> 00:14:21,739
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Waktu bedah, Waktu saat ini, Waktu pembiusan)</i></font>

165
00:14:21,739 --> 00:14:22,839
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tie.</i></font>

166
00:14:27,180 --> 00:14:28,349
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jack.</i></font>

167
00:14:32,089 --> 00:14:33,219
<font color=#FFFF00>Gunting.</font>

168
00:14:39,989 --> 00:14:41,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana?</font>

169
00:14:41,229 --> 00:14:45,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini operasi yang sulit,
tapi semuanya berjalan lancar sejauh ini.</font>

170
00:14:47,700 --> 00:14:48,800
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tie.</i></font>

171
00:15:06,389 --> 00:15:11,629
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Pusat Ruang Operasi)</i></font>

172
00:15:20,239 --> 00:15:22,839
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau cemas?
/ Tidak.</font>

173
00:15:23,300 --> 00:15:24,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Duduklah.</font>

174
00:15:26,410 --> 00:15:28,879
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini baru enam jam.</font>

175
00:15:28,879 --> 00:15:31,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bilang itu akan lebih dari 10 jam.</font>

176
00:15:31,280 --> 00:15:33,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ada masalah? Tunggu disini.</font>

177
00:15:33,210 --> 00:15:34,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan pergi dan memeriksa.</font>

178
00:15:35,119 --> 00:15:37,619
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bilang ini baru enam jam.</font>

179
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:43,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Inikah yang Hyun khawatirkan?</font>

180
00:15:43,629 --> 00:15:45,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia menyuruhku untuk menjagamu.</font>

181
00:15:45,560 --> 00:15:48,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bilang itu bisa semakin buruk bagimu.</font>

182
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,869
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia juga bilang begini.</font>

183
00:15:50,869 --> 00:15:52,570
<font color=#FFFF00><i>"Jika mereka tidak meneleponmu
selama prosedur...,"</i></font>

184
00:15:52,570 --> 00:15:54,900
<font color=#FFFF00><i>"Itu berarti operasinya berjalan lancar."</i></font>

185
00:15:54,900 --> 00:15:57,040
<font color=#FFFF00><i>"Jadi jangan cemas, dan cukup menunggu."</i></font>

186
00:15:58,040 --> 00:15:59,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu itu, 'kan?</font>

187
00:16:02,509 --> 00:16:05,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Duduklah. Mari kita istirahat.</font>

188
00:16:13,190 --> 00:16:16,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Minum ini. Aku memilih sesuatu
untuk menenangkanmu.</font>

189
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:22,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah dewasa.</font>

190
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter, darah.</font>

191
00:16:38,509 --> 00:16:40,249
<font color=#FFFF00>Darimana asalnya?</font>

192
00:16:41,349 --> 00:16:42,719
<font color=#FFFF00>Kim Jae Hwan, fokus.</font>

193
00:16:43,790 --> 00:16:46,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan bertanggung jawab
jika dia meninggal karena pendarahan?</font>

194
00:17:08,779 --> 00:17:10,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Tekanan darahnya turun.</font>

195
00:17:15,850 --> 00:17:17,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Di mana kebocorannya?</font>

196
00:17:18,019 --> 00:17:20,019
<font color=#FFFF00>Darimana asalnya?</font>

197
00:17:44,450 --> 00:17:47,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana hasilnya?</font>

198
00:17:52,890 --> 00:17:54,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Operasi...</font>

199
00:17:56,759 --> 00:17:58,789
<font color=#FFFF00>...berjalan sangat baik.</font>

200
00:18:03,799 --> 00:18:04,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak.</font>

201
00:18:07,140 --> 00:18:09,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami harus menunggu dan memeriksa...,</font>

202
00:18:09,069 --> 00:18:11,569
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi tumornya sudah benar-benar diangkat.</font>

203
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:15,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakak, Ayah akan hidup?</font>

204
00:18:15,940 --> 00:18:17,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia berhasil, kan?</font>

205
00:18:20,049 --> 00:18:22,819
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Ruang operasi)</i></font>

206
00:18:23,219 --> 00:18:25,749
<font color=#FFFF00>Pak Song. Pak Song?</font>

207
00:18:26,120 --> 00:18:27,819
<font color=#FFFF00>Sadarlah.</font>

208
00:18:28,019 --> 00:18:29,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Di mana kita?</font>

209
00:18:30,229 --> 00:18:32,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Pak Song. Pak Song.</font>

210
00:18:33,759 --> 00:18:34,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

211
00:18:35,799 --> 00:18:37,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, Ayah sudah sadar?</font>

212
00:18:37,799 --> 00:18:38,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

213
00:19:16,239 --> 00:19:17,809
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah selesai.</font>

214
00:19:29,120 --> 00:19:30,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah berhasil.</font>

215
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:54,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Eun Jae?</font>

216
00:19:56,110 --> 00:19:58,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda masih minum kopi manis setelah operasi?</font>

217
00:20:00,749 --> 00:20:03,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu saja. Itu benar-benar sudah berakhir.</font>

218
00:20:08,289 --> 00:20:10,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Dua sendok teh kopi, gula, dan krimer.</font>

219
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:11,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Tambah gula lagi?</font>

220
00:20:12,190 --> 00:20:14,299
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau tidak tenggelamkan aku
di gula saja?</font>

221
00:20:14,630 --> 00:20:16,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Punyaku tiga sendok teh gula.</font>

222
00:20:16,829 --> 00:20:18,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

223
00:20:26,410 --> 00:20:27,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau dan aku...</font>

224
00:20:28,710 --> 00:20:31,210
<font color=#FFFF00>...duduk berdampingan minum kopi manis...</font>

225
00:20:31,850 --> 00:20:34,350
<font color=#FFFF00>...setelah banyak operasi
yang tak terhitung jumlahnya.</font>

226
00:20:35,180 --> 00:20:37,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Kitai bekerja saling berlawanan...</font>

227
00:20:37,120 --> 00:20:39,249
<font color=#FFFF00>...pada banyak kasus juga.</font>

228
00:20:39,549 --> 00:20:41,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita bekerja dengan hebat bersama-sama.</font>

229
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:44,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda pemimpin yang hebat.</font>

230
00:20:49,430 --> 00:20:50,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku minta maaf.</font>

231
00:20:52,799 --> 00:20:54,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menghancur liburan...</font>

232
00:20:54,700 --> 00:20:56,799
<font color=#FFFF00>...dengan meminta bantuan Anda.</font>

233
00:20:58,039 --> 00:21:01,239
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak apa-apa. Sejak kapan kita bisa libur?</font>

234
00:21:16,930 --> 00:21:19,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu apa yang ingin kau katakan.</font>

235
00:21:19,729 --> 00:21:21,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak perlu berusaha keras.</font>

236
00:21:24,930 --> 00:21:26,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Profesor.</font>

237
00:21:28,739 --> 00:21:30,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

238
00:21:33,069 --> 00:21:35,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yang harus berterima kasih.</font>

239
00:21:36,279 --> 00:21:38,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau membuat keputusan yang lebih sulit.</font>

240
00:21:40,450 --> 00:21:41,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

241
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:45,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah mempercayakanku
untuk menjadi ahli bedah.</font>

242
00:21:48,289 --> 00:21:49,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

243
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:52,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan maaf.</font>

244
00:21:54,559 --> 00:21:57,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat dokter bedah membuat kesalahan
di ruang operasi...</font>

245
00:21:58,469 --> 00:21:59,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Sejujurnya...,</font>

246
00:22:00,340 --> 00:22:04,670
<font color=#FFFF00>...meskipun pasien dan keluarga
tidak akan pernah mau menerimanya...,</font>

247
00:22:06,340 --> 00:22:09,140
<font color=#FFFF00>...kesalahan dan kecelakaan
bisa terjadi selama operasi.</font>

248
00:22:09,809 --> 00:22:12,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter juga manusia.</font>

249
00:22:14,019 --> 00:22:16,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku berusaha untuk menutupi...</font>

250
00:22:16,479 --> 00:22:18,620
<font color=#FFFF00>...kesalahanku dan mengubur kebenaran.</font>

251
00:22:18,620 --> 00:22:20,259
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah kesalahannya.</font>

252
00:22:23,420 --> 00:22:25,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak tahu kenapa melakukan itu.</font>

253
00:22:29,529 --> 00:22:30,799
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku takut.</font>

254
00:22:31,900 --> 00:22:34,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya bisa memikirkan
tentang kehilangan sesuatu.</font>

255
00:22:35,039 --> 00:22:37,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Kritik dan serangan.</font>

256
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:39,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Reputasiku hancur.</font>

257
00:22:39,610 --> 00:22:41,809
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bisa membahayakan
jabatan dan gelarku.</font>

258
00:22:45,809 --> 00:22:47,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Inilah kesenangannya.</font>

259
00:22:50,180 --> 00:22:52,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah orang lain mengenaliku atau tidak...,</font>

260
00:22:52,850 --> 00:22:55,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bertindak seolah menjadi dewa
saat sedang menggunakan pisau bedah...</font>

261
00:22:56,819 --> 00:22:59,789
<font color=#FFFF00>....dan berkeringat sepanjang malam
di ruangan untuk menyelamatkan pasien.</font>

262
00:23:00,329 --> 00:23:02,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu meminum secangkir kopi manis murah.</font>

263
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:07,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pikir ini akan...</font>

264
00:23:07,999 --> 00:23:10,769
<font color=#FFFF00>...lebih dari cukup untuk membuatku lanjut.</font>

265
00:23:16,009 --> 00:23:17,809
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih untuk kopinya.</font>

266
00:23:18,950 --> 00:23:21,219
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku belum pernah
minum secangkir kopi seenak ini.</font>

267
00:23:22,549 --> 00:23:25,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harap bisa sering
menikmati ini suatu saat nanti.</font>

268
00:23:36,799 --> 00:23:39,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah banyak menderita
sejak aku mengasingkanmu.</font>

269
00:23:40,940 --> 00:23:43,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya kau harus datang kembali.</font>

270
00:23:43,969 --> 00:23:46,239
<font color=#FFFF00>Jang Sung Ho ingin kau kembali...,</font>

271
00:23:46,239 --> 00:23:48,079
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan direktur rumah sakit merasa tertekan.</font>

272
00:23:48,809 --> 00:23:51,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan dengan mudah
menjadi asisten profesor.</font>

273
00:23:51,509 --> 00:23:52,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi...
/ Tidak.</font>

274
00:23:54,450 --> 00:23:57,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin tinggal di kapal rumah sakit.</font>

275
00:23:57,390 --> 00:23:59,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingin tinggal? Kenapa?</font>

276
00:24:02,289 --> 00:24:04,259
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkin seperti Anda...,</font>

277
00:24:04,460 --> 00:24:08,529
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku ingin menjadi dewa
saat sedang memegang pisau bedah.</font>

278
00:24:10,299 --> 00:24:12,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku satu-satunya ahli bedah di kapal.</font>

279
00:24:12,870 --> 00:24:14,539
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku punya banyak peluang.</font>

280
00:24:15,739 --> 00:24:18,039
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?
/ Dan...</font>

281
00:24:19,309 --> 00:24:20,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan apa?</font>

282
00:24:21,380 --> 00:24:22,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Masih ada lagi?</font>

283
00:24:32,690 --> 00:24:34,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini dia.
/ Silakan.</font>

284
00:24:35,420 --> 00:24:37,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini?
/ Coba saja.</font>

285
00:24:37,289 --> 00:24:38,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia yang memasak semuanya.</font>

286
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:40,999
<font color=#FFFF00>Operasi berjalan lancar.</font>

287
00:24:40,999 --> 00:24:42,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus merayakan Chuseok.</font>

288
00:24:42,759 --> 00:24:44,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar, kita harus.
/ Terima kasih.</font>

289
00:24:45,370 --> 00:24:46,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya ampun.</font>

290
00:24:46,499 --> 00:24:49,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigoo, kau mengalahkanku.</font>

291
00:24:49,600 --> 00:24:51,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku membawa makanan juga.</font>

292
00:24:51,469 --> 00:24:52,739
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigoo.
/ Aku juga.</font>

293
00:24:53,039 --> 00:24:54,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua orang membawa makanan.</font>

294
00:24:54,910 --> 00:24:56,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bilang kalau kita
akan menjadi yang pertama.</font>

295
00:24:56,479 --> 00:24:59,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Kupikir semua orang akan datang nanti.</font>

296
00:24:59,150 --> 00:25:00,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigooo.
/ Di mana Eun Jae?</font>

297
00:25:01,049 --> 00:25:02,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sedang menemui profesor.</font>

298
00:25:02,380 --> 00:25:05,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa semua orang berencana
untuk berkumpul di sini?</font>

299
00:25:05,319 --> 00:25:08,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak semuanya.
/ Kita saling membaca pikiran.</font>

300
00:25:08,059 --> 00:25:09,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka seperti <i>The Three Musketeers</i>.</font>

301
00:25:09,690 --> 00:25:12,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka bahkan membawa kue.</font>

302
00:25:12,160 --> 00:25:14,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini sumpitnya.</font>

303
00:25:14,059 --> 00:25:16,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Semuanya, makan.
/ Betul.</font>

304
00:25:16,860 --> 00:25:19,769
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.
/ Terima kasih.</font>

305
00:25:20,069 --> 00:25:22,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Ngomong-ngomong, siapa dia?</font>

306
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:25,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo, aku Woo Jae, adik Eun Jae.</font>

307
00:25:25,009 --> 00:25:26,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau adiknya Dr. Song?
/ Iya.</font>

308
00:25:26,910 --> 00:25:28,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tampan.</font>

309
00:25:28,410 --> 00:25:30,710
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Perawat Yoo, kau bisa bernyanyi untuk kita?</i></font>

310
00:25:30,710 --> 00:25:33,410
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Nyanyikan.
/ Ayolah.</i></font>

311
00:25:33,410 --> 00:25:36,150
<font color=#FFFF00>1, 2, 1, 2, 3.</font>

312
00:25:36,150 --> 00:25:38,620
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ini Chuseok, ini Chuseok.</i></font>

313
00:25:39,019 --> 00:25:40,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu keren.</font>

314
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:44,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita bernyanyi bersama.</font>

315
00:25:48,900 --> 00:25:50,100
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ambil sendiri.</i></font>

316
00:26:34,479 --> 00:26:36,309
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Oh Hye Jung)</i></font>

317
00:26:48,190 --> 00:26:49,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu?</font>

318
00:26:51,860 --> 00:26:55,299
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu di samping foto ibumu?</font>

319
00:26:56,059 --> 00:26:58,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu foto keluarga kita.</font>

320
00:26:58,670 --> 00:27:00,769
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menaruhnya di sana untuk Ibu.</font>

321
00:27:03,840 --> 00:27:05,309
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapan itu?</font>

322
00:27:05,410 --> 00:27:08,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu di taman hiburan 100 hari
setelah Woo Jae lahir.</font>

323
00:27:11,180 --> 00:27:12,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kau ingat?</font>

324
00:27:14,620 --> 00:27:15,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu pertama kalinya kita...</font>

325
00:27:17,090 --> 00:27:18,719
<font color=#FFFF00>...ke taman hiburan.</font>

326
00:27:19,150 --> 00:27:21,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu juga foto pertama keluarga kita.</font>

327
00:27:23,319 --> 00:27:25,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya itu yang pertama
dan terakhir.</font>

328
00:27:27,960 --> 00:27:29,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu bukan yang terakhir kalinya.</font>

329
00:27:29,900 --> 00:27:31,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita akan berfoto setiap hari.</font>

330
00:27:32,900 --> 00:27:35,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, berbalik.</font>

331
00:27:36,569 --> 00:27:38,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Kesini. Kak, kesini sekarang.</font>

332
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:40,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sedang apa?
/ Kemari.</font>

333
00:27:41,479 --> 00:27:42,809
<font color=#FFFF00>Berdiri di sini.</font>

334
00:27:43,039 --> 00:27:44,749
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa dia belum datang?</font>

335
00:27:46,479 --> 00:27:47,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo, Hyun.</font>

336
00:27:48,579 --> 00:27:49,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau kemari?</font>

337
00:27:50,789 --> 00:27:51,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf karena terlambat.</font>

338
00:27:52,249 --> 00:27:54,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus membawa kamera dari Seoul.</font>

339
00:27:54,660 --> 00:27:58,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau jauh-jauh pergi ke Seoul?
Kamera apapun tidak masalah.</font>

340
00:27:58,489 --> 00:28:01,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak mungkin. Kau sudah lama
tidak berfoto keluarga.</font>

341
00:28:03,600 --> 00:28:05,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Bersiaplah. Aku akan mengambil foto.</font>

342
00:28:06,069 --> 00:28:07,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

343
00:28:07,900 --> 00:28:08,969
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Oh Hye Jung)</i></font>

344
00:28:14,380 --> 00:28:15,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa tersenyum?</font>

345
00:28:16,640 --> 00:28:19,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan bertempur? Wajahmu sangat suram.</font>

346
00:28:20,450 --> 00:28:21,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayolah, Kak.</font>

347
00:28:22,749 --> 00:28:23,989
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Smile.</i></font>

348
00:28:38,799 --> 00:28:40,640
<font color=#FFFF00><i>1, 2, 3.</i></font>

